title: Life expectancy at birth in Germany 2017
yAxis: Life expectancy at birth in years
summary: Overall Life expectancy at birth in years has increased over the Year.
Life expectancy at birth in years is slightly decreasing from 2013 to 2015.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 2013 and 2014.
The highest Life expectancy at birth in years, of value 81.09 was reached at Year 2014
Minimum Life expectancy at birth in years about 80.49 was reached at Year 2013
